title: MILLION DOLLAZ WORTH OF GAME EP:98 "NOT INVITED TO THE BRUNCH" FEATURING FUNK FLEX
description:
Hot 97 DJ Funk Flex comes onto Million Dollaz Worth Of Game and discusses his favorite rappers of all time, his relationship with DJ Clue, gives advice to up-and-coming artist and more!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/mworthofgame
